headline: ICE Earnings: Profit Margin Expansion Reinforces Bullish Narratives
summary: Intercontinental Exchange (ICE) posted robust earnings growth of 29.8% over the past year, a pronounced turnaround from its prior five-year annual average of -0.7%. Net profit margins climbed to 31% from 26.3% last year, highlighting a clear improvement in profitability.
